summary: 56 free perks, all skills 100. Primary: Archery, one handed, destruction, although you can make him into any kind of character. I recommend him for a lvl 82 base, use showracemenu and change him up.
descriptionHtml:
56 perks available. All skills maxed. I used player.addperk <perkID> for a number of perks, and used prerequisites, but you\'ll be able to pretty much make any of the skills of your choice utterly maxed. Completed Thieves Guild, working on Companions and not much else. This character is open for mass killing sprees of the helpless children of Skyrim.

Health 390 + ?
Magic 427 ?
Stamina 200 ?

Recommended mods that I use with Alnthlam.

LOTR Weapons Collection - Isilmeriel
Killable Children - Xylozi
Faster Arrows - Fordperfect
No Perk Prerequisites -  ClassicalNoodle
ENB series v 1.06 - BorisVoronstov
